   <p>
<span class="docSource"><span class="dType"><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipients copy (A recipients copy is assumed to be in the hand of the signer unless it is otherwise described.) ]">RC</abbr></span> (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>); addressed: His Exy John Adams Esqr Amsterdam To the Care of Mess. Fizeaux &amp; Grand.; endorsed: Dr Franklins Letter concerning, Charges and Expences.; by John Thaxter: June 11th. 1781 A. 4th. Oct. 1781.</span>
</p>

</div>
